3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel attention mechanism to address the issue of outliers impairing global context in mismatch removal networks. Attention mechanisms are commonly used in artificial intelligence applications, which suggests that this paper could belong to the AI sub-category.
